#. <section class="sutta" id="an6.83"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an6.83:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an6.83:0.2"
msgid "8. Arahattavagga"
msgstr "8. Perfection"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an6.83:0.3"
msgid "83. Aggadhammasutta"
msgstr "83. The Best Thing"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an6.83:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo aggaṃ dhammaṃ "
"arahattaṃ sacchikātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, a mendicant with six qualities can’t realize the best thing, "
"perfection."

msgctxt "an6.83:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.83:1.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu assaddho hoti, ahiriko hoti, anottappī hoti, kusīto "
"hoti, duppañño hoti, kāye ca jīvite ca sāpekkho hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant is faithless, shameless, imprudent, lazy, and witless. "
"And they’re concerned with their body and their life."

msgctxt "an6.83:1.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu abhabbo aggaṃ "
"dhammaṃ arahattaṃ sacchikātuṃ."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these six qualities can’t realize the best thing, "
"perfection."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.434"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an6.83:2.1"
msgid ""
"Chahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo aggaṃ dhammaṃ "
"arahattaṃ sacchikātuṃ."
msgstr "A mendicant with six qualities can realize the best thing, perfection."

msgctxt "an6.83:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi chahi?"
msgstr "What six?"

msgctxt "an6.83:2.3"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu saddho hoti, hirīmā hoti, ottappī hoti, "
"āraddhavīriyo hoti, paññavā hoti, kāye ca jīvite ca anapekkho hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant is faithful, conscientious, prudent, energetic, and "
"wise. And they have no concern for their body and their life."

msgctxt "an6.83:2.4"
msgid ""
"Imehi kho, bhikkhave, chahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu bhabbo aggaṃ "
"dhammaṃ arahattaṃ sacchikātun”ti."
msgstr ""
"A mendicant with these six qualities can realize the best thing, perfection.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an6.83:2.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
